post_text:
Teachers, staff and principal Mr. Meunier from Emma C. Smith Elementary paraded through neighborhoods where students live to give a social distancing "hello!" Students and families made signs and waved as the procession went by. #SuperintendentKellyBowers and her dog Boomer even escorted the Smith Cougar through the parade!

Check out our Livermore Schools Instagram for pictures from today's parade! https://www.instagram.com/livermoreschools/?hl=en

@emmasmithpta

